  "texts": [
    "Mechanisms and pathways associated with wound healing have indeed been pointed as being implicated in cancer proliferation and metastasis 70, 71.",
    "We also showed that such a method can be used to answer multicancer types questions.",
    "First, we assessed its ability to distinguish adenocarcinoma (LUAD) from squamous cell carcinoma (LUSC).",
    "The TCGA cohort was used as a training set and an independent cohort from NYU, (NYU 2), was used as an independent cohort.",
    "The average AUC of 0.99 is even better than results previously obtained by training Inception-V3 on analogous external cohorts 8."
  ]
}